reference "eq:share-frailty-model"

\end_inset

 is of known parametric form up to a few unknown parameters.
 The proposed package, an implementation of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "gorfine2006prospective"

\end_inset

, does not make this assumption; the baseline hazard function is unspecified
 and estimated non-parametrically.
\end_layout

